8a1225ffb9f4bf000ce5","tid":1257740,"uid":268358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T17:58:18.000Z","msg":"問下醫生打針先<br />\n我上次係打針止左瀉，再食其他藥訓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:04:34.000Z","msg":"不過我上次唔記得係感冒菌入腸定腸胃炎，總之都係玩左幾日 頂唔順。 你可以試下問問醫生你個情況可唔可以打針止左先？我上次前後玩左5日，<br />\n一開始都有發燒，成個人唔舒服到食粥都食幾啖要趴低休息"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:21:24.000Z","msg":"太遲了，我出左院，今次公院太多人等床位，冇得留院觀察。醫生打左支止痛針、吊鹽水同比埋藥就放我走。好奇怪，除左7-8號嘔吐冇胃口，之後我食慾係完全冇問題架，食成碗飯都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"263c661c9e0c64e8ccc2b7848b839fb5f66a99a7","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b283b25565071c490ebae0a5cc7db63d380222fb","tid":1257740,"uid":18821,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:08:17.000Z","msg":"Crohn&rsquo;s disease or ulcerative colitis?<br />\n就咁症狀係有啲似,但有驗過血冇理由睇唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問其他身體症狀,眼有冇紅/痛<br />\n身體有冇地方無啦啦瘀咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:26:15.000Z","msg":"唉，我就係擔心呢兩個病，都有過懷疑，好似係冇藥可根治，只可食藥控制，成世都跟住。以後冇得食譚仔麻辣、pizza、壽司...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n眼冇紅冇痛，瘀都冇，除左腹痛肚痾，其餘一切正常。"},{"pid":"2b11494f624e5dd39bd847870be6cba21339fa25","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67c780eb7b8de683920fbcf580e58b2fcf8fef06","tid":1257740,"uid":18821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b283b25565071c490ebae0a5cc7db63d380222fb","tid":1257740,"uid":18821,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:08:17.000Z","msg":"Crohn&rsquo;s disease or ulcerative colitis?<br />\n就咁症狀係有啲似,但有驗過血冇理由睇唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問其他身體症狀,眼有冇紅/痛<br />\n身體有冇地方無啦啦瘀咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:11:27.000Z","msg":"同埋最近有冇出過國？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:26:26.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"c3edd8d20d59b59f66fcec171f1b25f380bbc17f","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e6e21d63ad4ac1eb64e40cecc1264ef54950fd4","tid":1257740,"uid":18821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67c780eb7b8de683920fbcf580e58b2fcf8fef06","tid":1257740,"uid":18821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b283b25565071c490ebae0a5cc7db63d380222fb","tid":1257740,"uid":18821,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:08:17.000Z","msg":"Crohn&rsquo;s disease or ulcerative colitis?<br />\n就咁症狀係有啲似,但有驗過血冇理由睇唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問其他身體症狀,眼有冇紅/痛<br />\n身體有冇地方無啦啦瘀咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:11:27.000Z","msg":"同埋最近有冇出過國？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:14:37.000Z","msg":"除咗上述嘅藥,自己有冇食開咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屋企人有冇呢啲問題？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:29:59.000Z","msg":"食過胃藥（胃的素），nikp-rabeprazole ec tab 20mg，強力胃藥，仲有隻醫消化性潰瘍既，唔記得名"},{"pid":"658420bcb84eee1ccccaad13d92b91ffe00d3312","tid":1257740,"uid":268358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:39:30.000Z","msg":"如果係腸胃炎 食胃藥幫助唔大喎🤔<br />\n你會唔會係最近食野都唔算清淡？我上次睇醫生佢連寶礦力都唔比我飲 佢話我個情況飲完會再瀉過 忍下口飲水係最好 食粥都只可以係栗米粥 最多"},{"pid":"231abb6bb5d7c28c9ed5004a0123b739f62f2fb8","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6bed0572289d00c10325fbfe91ec987c0681f01","tid":1257740,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:15:24.000Z","msg":"same 痛到仆街 已經第三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:40:45.000Z","msg":"同病相憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痾嘔都還好<br />\n腹痛果下難頂<br />\n陰啲陰啲咁那住咁<br />\n人地問邊到痛又講唔清楚<br />\n<br />\nBtw 琴日朝早個肚feel到腸道蠕動好快，kick住左某個位，開始肚脹，然後有明顯既痛楚，又痾返，我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582933a48d78dd52c564332977398328cf0f3f07","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"658420bcb84eee1ccccaad13d92b91ffe00d3312","tid":1257740,"uid":268358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:39:30.000Z","msg":"如果係腸胃炎 食胃藥幫助唔大喎🤔<br />\n你會唔會係最近食野都唔算清淡？我上次睇醫生佢連寶礦力都唔比我飲 佢話我個情況飲完會再瀉過 忍下口飲水係最好 食粥都只可以係栗米粥 最多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:51:49.000Z","msg":"因為8號退燒冇痾嘔後開始肚脹、心口間中刺痛似比火燒，以為係胃病，連專科都比我呃左，所以期間有keep住食自己/醫生比既胃藥。<br />\n<br />\n呢段時間我日日食白粥同消化餅，飲食定時，少量多餐。係呢兩日開始食番米飯，但都多菜少肉。琴日又開始痾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2df4af54abadd94689a5dfb68ce4815066c6ca","tid":1257740,"uid":86222,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b283b25565071c490ebae0a5cc7db63d380222fb","tid":1257740,"uid":18821,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:08:17.000Z","msg":"Crohn&rsquo;s disease or ulcerative colitis?<br />\n就咁症狀係有啲似,但有驗過血冇理由睇唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問其他身體症狀,眼有冇紅/痛<br />\n身體有冇地方無啦啦瘀咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T19:48:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得似IBD多啲"},{"pid":"08c74579eb16336b6c39f06264319289fe66d777","tid":1257740,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T20:56:30.000Z","msg":"又痛醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3028aeed95630ca1807ad0a3061e8481689d49fb","tid":1257740,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08c74579eb16336b6c39f06264319289fe66d777","tid":1257740,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T20:56:30.000Z","msg":"又痛醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20100325/large/25la3p99n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20100325%2Flarge%2F25la3p99n.jpg&h=ef5b57f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d05c5da160377885033e417f135f32dd345516b","tid":1257740,"uid":269413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:34:05.000Z","msg":"屌。。驗血都驗到病毒或細菌感染。照胃鏡又無事。咁L出奇"},{"pid":"fd957d128dadf47df92a14b1c8fed61e7bb129d0","tid":1257740,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T23:02:44.000Z","msg":"平日多唔多食甜野？"},{"pid":"cafc9ddfddc571ed42a237ccecd9d2673ceb93fb","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd2df4af54abadd94689a5dfb68ce4815066c6ca","tid":1257740,"uid":86222,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b283b25565071c490ebae0a5cc7db63d380222fb","tid":1257740,"uid":18821,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:08:17.000Z","msg":"Crohn&rsquo;s disease or ulcerative colitis?<br />\n就咁症狀係有啲似,但有驗過血冇理由睇唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問其他身體症狀,眼有冇紅/痛<br />\n身體有冇地方無啦啦瘀咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T19:48:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得似IBD多啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:34:03.000Z","msg":"IBD 同 Crohn&rsquo;s disease or ulcerative colitis 有咩分別，我見患者都有好多併發症，但我都冇wo。希望唔係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa4500ae06790a9c7c90e607f92898fe9fa14a16","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08c74579eb16336b6c39f06264319289fe66d777","tid":1257740,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T20:56:30.000Z","msg":"又痛醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:37:37.000Z","msg":"琴晚訓到，唔知咩事，又止左痾，但多屁同間中腸嗚，依然係feel到肚唔舒服，但唔係腹痛，個肚係好似條筋比人扯住既感覺，唔知幾時又痛返。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fed3158e7a10194f191907a886c7b752d527b4f","tid":1257740,"uid":159414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:40:26.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痾咗成個星期<br />\n中途有發燒，有好轉<br />\n但都仲係痾同肚痛<br />\n不過無睇醫生<br />\n反正佢都係話痾乾淨就無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4707293127f3b7f17bd41e457ecde7a481186c","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d05c5da160377885033e417f135f32dd345516b","tid":1257740,"uid":269413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T21:34:05.000Z","msg":"屌。。驗血都驗到病毒或細菌感染。照胃鏡又無事。咁L出奇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:43:42.000Z","msg":"可能真係腸胃敏感呢，不過琴日前前後後痾左12-15次，有冇咁嚴重<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係痾水，係痾左啲唔成形又多泡既爛屎，有時量多有時量少，多屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b196b8a40115bbb41a0771104f9bc4a210abe806","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd957d128dadf47df92a14b1c8fed61e7bb129d0","tid":1257740,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T23:02:44.000Z","msg":"平日多唔多食甜野？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:44:12.000Z","msg":"多呀 成日食零食"},{"pid":"7898d78cacee08cefa6b29c9902a083265435942","tid":1257740,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:45:27.000Z","msg":"唔知樓上點解咁快諗IBD <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇番樓主病歷，其實個病情係有啲反覆，腸胃不適，食完藥好番左啲，未斷晒尾，又差番咁，維持大概兩星期左右<br />\n<br />\n有時腸胃炎真係無咁快好，亦都要睇你戒口戒成點<br />\n<br />\n連屎都驗埋，有惡菌應該一早通知左你。當然屎仲有其他野可以驗，而公立醫院上次可能只係做最初步既檢查<br />\n<br />\n西藥方面，你睇過咁多醫生，連專科都睇埋，我諗最好既藥你都食過，唔使多講<br />\n<br />\n坊間既藥之中，我試過釣魚牌係work<br />\n<br />\n要診斷IBD都好靠照腸鏡，抽血都驗唔到啲咩，所以等專科安排啦"},{"pid":"898b93e3f460c559507aac41d5c202681ffb5477","tid":1257740,"uid":268516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b196b8a40115bbb41a0771104f9bc4a210abe806","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd957d128dadf47df92a14b1c8fed61e7bb129d0","tid":1257740,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T23:02:44.000Z","msg":"平日多唔多食甜野？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:44:12.000Z","msg":"多呀 成日食零食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:50:25.000Z","msg":"試吓戒糖戒一兩星期<br />\n對我嚟講好work"},{"pid":"ec344ee535ac0788ea4c63cba46ae1e6bab38bcf","tid":1257740,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:57:28.000Z","msg":"頂唔順了 請假睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b497334621b5be5acd14d8e75f5ebb7e06a467e","tid":1257740,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"人人唔同 我試過腸胃炎痾嘔三四日 好返哂<br />\n又試過痾成個幾星期 痾到無野痾都仲痾緊"},{"pid":"e847e1a9eb546721c25035e3a61901aa33dadc8b","tid":1257740,"uid":164534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec344ee535ac0788ea4c63cba46ae1e6bab38bcf","tid":1257740,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:57:28.000Z","msg":"頂唔順了 請假睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:02:29.000Z","msg":"真心 照腸鏡<br />\n我前幾日照完"},{"pid":"78ed77f7cce2f3301880bbd15a055703c1309f20","tid":1257740,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:03:11.000Z","msg":"睇開果個幾好要就留tg"},{"pid":"d2174b8cc207efb8c66ac4c2b55bbe7b3a92fb21","tid":1257740,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:05:54.000Z","msg":"腸鏡先係最有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過最辛苦"},{"pid":"399b83192f027a670149f13eb8945f555ee6c377","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7898d78cacee08cefa6b29c9902a083265435942","tid":1257740,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:45:27.000Z","msg":"唔知樓上點解咁快諗IBD <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇番樓主病歷，其實個病情係有啲反覆，腸胃不適，食完藥好番左啲，未斷晒尾，又差番咁，維持大概兩星期左右<br />\n<br />\n有時腸胃炎真係無咁快好，亦都要睇你戒口戒成點<br />\n<br />\n連屎都驗埋，有惡菌應該一早通知左你。當然屎仲有其他野可以驗，而公立醫院上次可能只係做最初步既檢查<br />\n<br />\n西藥方面，你睇過咁多醫生，連專科都睇埋，我諗最好既藥你都食過，唔使多講<br />\n<br />\n坊間既藥之中，我試過釣魚牌係work<br />\n<br />\n要診斷IBD都好靠照腸鏡，抽血都驗唔到啲咩，所以等專科安排啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:06:15.000Z","msg":"合理呀，唔似咁IBD嚴重，照腸應該走唔甩，遲早都要check下買個安心。依家唯有再去專科覆診再問下情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c0461a834442d470dbe1e2f822dde14ccd78b1","tid":1257740,"uid":200417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:07:09.000Z","msg":"點解照胃鏡唔連腸鏡一齊照？<br />\n<br />\n利申上年因有住院保，入院留晚第二朝照腸鏡胃鏡，會有麻醉，訓個靚覺做完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後一蚊都唔駛俾"},{"pid":"7cb2ef2669a7f314a7fab0622bdc138f85d63fa4","tid":1257740,"uid":109918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:07:22.000Z","msg":"係咪慢性盲腸炎呀？我之前都好似你咁 不斷胃痛肚痾嘔 斷斷續續半年 但照x光胃鏡都係無事 最後入左急症照磁力共振 先發現係慢性盲腸炎要即刻做手術"},{"pid":"6ebda6371db350801f111e8071cbfac0c1716276","tid":1257740,"uid":124268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:09:26.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇幾聲咳？如果有可能會係腸結核<br />\n<br />\n同埋屙得好勁果陣一定要食止屙藥，屙清D菌固之然好，但太勁會流失太多水份，身體差難好返惡性循環。<br />\n<br />\n有冇試過食D益生菌片(唔好飲益力多)，應該會有少少幫助"},{"pid":"a5af4dbb5f2b1505c8a261c8afcd488585307ffe","tid":1257740,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:10:26.000Z","msg":"有無諗過屋企嘅水/食物衛生有問題"},{"pid":"6b4fd84d161d3f98d5735db1c00b6da1434996e6","tid":1257740,"uid":91897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:10:38.000Z","msg":"上個月痾左成個星期屎水<br />\n第一日睇完家庭醫生，無好轉反而嚴重左<br />\n第二日一早就去左急症睇，去到原來發緊燒自己都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，開左消炎藥同抗生素，邊食藥邊痾清佢，最後差唔多一個幾星期先正常返<br />\n期間個人勁虛，起碼痾左3X次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />靠飲寶礦水為生"},{"pid":"f29c6664d14fc39a92925e44afba7295af8b1b77","tid":1257740,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:11:54.000Z","msg":"同女朋友一齊腸胃炎....我就發燒, 屙(輕微). 我女朋友咩都齊...<br />\n我已經得返屙..女朋友未好過, 第3日...<br />\n應該係間餐廳有問題, 報左1823<br />\n食環同衛生署話會跟進"},{"pid":"9c5ee2f0f82d58863657db65747c5a49b2f3be1a","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec344ee535ac0788ea4c63cba46ae1e6bab38bcf","tid":1257740,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:57:28.000Z","msg":"頂唔順了 請假睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:14:37.000Z","msg":"去睇啦，睇完至少安心啲。除非發燒，醫生通常會叫你買支1:1寶礦力，比啲止痛退燒，有需要時服既止痾止嘔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cbfc975f5512e5123ccc28e92e7f30a3487ffb","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"898b93e3f460c559507aac41d5c202681ffb5477","tid":1257740,"uid":268516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b196b8a40115bbb41a0771104f9bc4a210abe806","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd957d128dadf47df92a14b1c8fed61e7bb129d0","tid":1257740,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T23:02:44.000Z","msg":"平日多唔多食甜野？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:44:12.000Z","msg":"多呀 成日食零食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:50:25.000Z","msg":"試吓戒糖戒一兩星期<br />\n對我嚟講好work"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:18:00.000Z","msg":"依家日日白粥，消化餅，呢兩日先開始食米飯，仍然好清淡，就黎味覺喪失<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac406484fd6cb2cd38ba95e4745dcf5443b6daa","tid":1257740,"uid":89558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:21:18.000Z","msg":"i know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係要試過腸胃炎先會明 日日痾嘔再發燒 真係人間地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d916466f87c4e7475c2d00087b378454979cfe","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b497334621b5be5acd14d8e75f5ebb7e06a467e","tid":1257740,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"人人唔同 我試過腸胃炎痾嘔三四日 好返哂<br />\n又試過痾成個幾星期 痾到無野痾都仲痾緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:26:10.000Z","msg":"I know that feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係斷斷續續，7-8號狂痾，之後停左，只有腹脹腹部悶痛，係琴日又開始痾到hihi"},{"pid":"2b737ee451791652df7d6d58eb7f53495b73bec7","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2174b8cc207efb8c66ac4c2b55bbe7b3a92fb21","tid":1257740,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:05:54.000Z","msg":"腸鏡先係最有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過最辛苦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:27:35.000Z","msg":"公院腸鏡不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n私家麻醉完訓著左，照完都唔知發生咩事"},{"pid":"1f75869eca3536918641789ab4461888ec791940","tid":1257740,"uid":63452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cafc9ddfddc571ed42a237ccecd9d2673ceb93fb","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd2df4af54abadd94689a5dfb68ce4815066c6ca","tid":1257740,"uid":86222,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b283b25565071c490ebae0a5cc7db63d380222fb","tid":1257740,"uid":18821,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T18:08:17.000Z","msg":"Crohn&rsquo;s disease or ulcerative colitis?<br />\n就咁症狀係有啲似,但有驗過血冇理由睇唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問其他身體症狀,眼有冇紅/痛<br />\n身體有冇地方無啦啦瘀咗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T19:48:20.000Z","msg":"我覺得似IBD多啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:34:03.000Z","msg":"IBD 同 Crohn&rsquo;s disease or ulcerative colitis 有咩分別，我見患者都有好多併發症，但我都冇wo。希望唔係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:31:22.000Z","msg":"inflammatory bowel disease 咪就係Crohn's disease 同ulcerative colitis 嘅統稱"},{"pid":"459032a4a6a64de6491d766125b69e2efa258c7b","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77c0461a834442d470dbe1e2f822dde14ccd78b1","tid":1257740,"uid":200417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:07:09.000Z","msg":"點解照胃鏡唔連腸鏡一齊照？<br />\n<br />\n利申上年因有住院保，入院留晚第二朝照腸鏡胃鏡，會有麻醉，訓個靚覺做完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後一蚊都唔駛俾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:32:41.000Z","msg":"專科醫生唔比照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係腸胃炎，照腸會有危險，而且佢診斷我係胃病，都難怪佢，除左琴日痾返，之前keep住肚脹腹痛心口hing，我都以為係胃，所以只係照左胃 and 肝膽腎超聲波，超聲波過幾日覆診出報告。到時再睇下佢有咩follow-up。"},{"pid":"1ba959db81225447cf9702111be51d6277afb2ca","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cb2ef2669a7f314a7fab0622bdc138f85d63fa4","tid":1257740,"uid":109918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:07:22.000Z","msg":"係咪慢性盲腸炎呀？我之前都好似你咁 不斷胃痛肚痾嘔 斷斷續續半年 但照x光胃鏡都係無事 最後入左急症照磁力共振 先發現係慢性盲腸炎要即刻做手術"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:34:37.000Z","msg":"唔會掛，盲腸炎應該會集中係右下腹，而且按壓會痛，但檢查果陣醫生按壓我完全唔痛。"},{"pid":"bf9f9925e8487df6002f82ff5e02cfcafa8f1608","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ebda6371db350801f111e8071cbfac0c1716276","tid":1257740,"uid":124268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:09:26.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇幾聲咳？如果有可能會係腸結核<br />\n<br />\n同埋屙得好勁果陣一定要食止屙藥，屙清D菌固之然好，但太勁會流失太多水份，身體差難好返惡性循環。<br />\n<br />\n有冇試過食D益生菌片(唔好飲益力多)，應該會有少少幫助"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:38:48.000Z","msg":"冇呀，入急症果陣醫生都有check過<br />\n<br />\n真呀，7-8號我就係由得佢痾，一邊狂隊保礦力，一日痾左廿幾次，痾到勁虛弱，諗返起果陣應該要食止痾藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇，有咩推介"},{"pid":"8d8427ebb7853657c13db563e83cbd7eae920b65","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5af4dbb5f2b1505c8a261c8afcd488585307ffe","tid":1257740,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:10:26.000Z","msg":"有無諗過屋企嘅水/食物衛生有問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:41:43.000Z","msg":"有，我懷疑係食錯野搞到食物中毒，病發前屋企人朝早留左份pizza比我，我番去食完就出事。但唔肯定關唔關事，潛伏期可以好長。"},{"pid":"c37c3016df876410346c01c4c4c004c824b743f5","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b4fd84d161d3f98d5735db1c00b6da1434996e6","tid":1257740,"uid":91897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:10:38.000Z","msg":"上個月痾左成個星期屎水<br />\n第一日睇完家庭醫生，無好轉反而嚴重左<br />\n第二日一早就去左急症睇，去到原來發緊燒自己都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，開左消炎藥同抗生素，邊食藥邊痾清佢，最後差唔多一個幾星期先正常返<br />\n期間個人勁虛，起碼痾左3X次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />靠飲寶礦水為生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:46:37.000Z","msg":"3X次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屎忽都出血<br />\n發燒係感染得幾嚴重<br />\n我7-8號都係<br />\n食完抗生素之後就冇發過<br />\n只係一直唔斷尾"},{"pid":"1b1797ca98ba2680d0a76e491fbb2703000131f9","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f29c6664d14fc39a92925e44afba7295af8b1b77","tid":1257740,"uid":32934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:11:54.000Z","msg":"同女朋友一齊腸胃炎....我就發燒, 屙(輕微). 我女朋友咩都齊...<br />\n我已經得返屙..女朋友未好過, 第3日...<br />\n應該係間餐廳有問題, 報左1823<br />\n食環同衛生署話會跟進"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:48:13.000Z","msg":"係呀，兩個一齊，應該係食物中毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f203bc2bba208ac1a4fdaac229b9e34b8cd0300","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aac406484fd6cb2cd38ba95e4745dcf5443b6daa","tid":1257740,"uid":89558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:21:18.000Z","msg":"i know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係要試過腸胃炎先會明 日日痾嘔再發燒 真係人間地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T03:50:48.000Z","msg":"然後再清茶淡飯，人間煉獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8af2e778dd07a44308547ddd7ee67fedaca8d94","tid":1257740,"uid":109918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1ba959db81225447cf9702111be51d6277afb2ca","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like"