":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T12:53:49.000Z","msg":"上兩個星期又係腸胃炎<br />\n屙到仆街，抆屎抆到屎眼痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩星期輕左6kg<br />\n堅持住呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:43:02.000Z","msg":"6kg 好癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nChing唔舒服左兩星期？"},{"pid":"6202a09244eb44ad2d40561cfd1972ab93e3a503","tid":1257740,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T22:12:35.000Z","msg":"廠已入 唔知幾時先出得院<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6beb74c398293bb763be0e82787d98908e67918","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T08:12:04.000Z","msg":"上返水，專科覆診完，佢都擔心會係Ulcerative Colitis，但我冇就明顯既症狀：痾血便，而且起碼要持續2個月先診斷到。佢話暫時睇大機會係細菌性腸炎，有時痾唔清會持續咁耐，由佢痾清先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家我冇再痾水/多泡，大便變番長條形，但依然好易肚痛左下腹痛，坐係廁所等勁耐都痾唔出，好啦起身再等陣，終於痾到，痾完都仲係有便意，好困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家唔敢食咁飽，盡量食啲易消化食物，希望過多一排腸道正常返，求下你唔好再咁易肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca94cc737dcc611199f37ff34e43cd598f23d23","tid":1257740,"uid":181769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6202a09244eb44ad2d40561cfd1972ab93e3a503","tid":1257740,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T22:12:35.000Z","msg":"廠已入 唔知幾時先出得院<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T08:12:46.000Z","msg":"Ching 最近點"},{"pid":"65e08c1849541fecc4094cdb00861fe2352183c5","tid":1257740,"uid":83373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20